  "detailed_description": "\"Dream Hotel Master\" is a delightful casual simulation management game that puts you in charge of your own hotel empire! Play as multiple characters and experience the joy of hotel management, from running day-to-day operations to expanding your business and growing your hotel chain. With charming 2D graphics, intuitive controls, and endless strategic choices, become the ultimate hotel tycoon!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Play as multiple characters </strong></li></ul>Manage the front desk, guide the staff, optimize room layouts, decorate the hotel, and more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/aedc01c558ec585afe450c1a5a45439b.poster.avif?t=1715567195\" width=586 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/aedc01c558ec585afe450c1a5a45439b.webm?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/aedc01c558ec585afe450c1a5a45439b.mp4?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Expand your business</strong> </li></ul>Develop new services, organize events to attract guests, and establish partnerships.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/e704485a7342c0fc3d4c8ad36afe9221.poster.avif?t=1715567195\" width=586 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/e704485a7342c0fc3d4c8ad36afe9221.webm?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/e704485a7342c0fc3d4c8ad36afe9221.mp4?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Grow your hotel empire</strong></li></ul>Build more branches in the city and become the hotel tycoon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/9774dad9b3d52c3e2fb5138f58e7c1be.poster.avif?t=1715567195\" width=586 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/9774dad9b3d52c3e2fb5138f58e7c1be.webm?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/9774dad9b3d52c3e2fb5138f58e7c1be.mp4?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Rich gameplay</strong></li></ul>Challenge mode, endless mode, special events, and more, offering endless fun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/9822b551bbb7d22f2590b4a1e9c5fa41.poster.avif?t=1715567195\" width=586 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/9822b551bbb7d22f2590b4a1e9c5fa41.webm?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2951740/extras/9822b551bbb7d22f2590b4a1e9c5fa41.mp4?t=1715567195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience \"Dream Hotel Master\" and become the most popular hotel tycoon, creating your dream hotel empire today!",
